<font class="fromWhereText">
from Boston
</font>
</br>
<font class="bodyTextNarrow">
Take Storrow Drive to the
Anderson Bridge exit. Bear right
across Anderson Bridge, and drive
straight into Harvard Square. Just
before you enter Harvard Square,
turn left onto Brattle Street, then
follow it around to the right. After
you bear right, the first turn on
your right is Church Street.
</font>
</br>


<% End Select %>

