from I-90, Massachusetts Turnpike
</font>
</br>
<font class="bodyTextNarrow">
Get off at exit 18, Cambridge.
Turn left immediately onto Storrow
Drive westbound. Take the
Harvard Square exit and drive
straight towards Harvard Square.
Just before you enter Harvard
Square, turn left onto Brattle
Street, follow it around to the
right. After you bear right, the
first turn on your right is Church
Street.
</font>

